item.title: Help me to chgange starter kit
item.dc:creator: @tonypker13 tonypker13
item.description:
@tonypker13 wrote:

[quote=“warrick, post:4, topic:31466”][quote author=Mightylizard link=topic=45843.msg2563665#msg2563665 date=1228272975]
Ok well…

Go into Client.Java and search Starter or whatever your command is for starter…
Now below you should see something like this:

addItem(995, 15000000); addItem(392, 5000); addItem(554, 5000); addItem(555, 5000); addItem(565, 5000); addItem(556, 5000); addItem(557, 5000); addItem(560, 5000); addItem(561, 5000); addItem(562, 5000); addItem(563, 5000); addItem(566, 5000); addItem(558, 5000); addItem(892, 5000);

addItem(####, $$$$)

= Item ID

$ = Item Amount
[/quote]

mmh dunno where to find client.java in my 508 client??[/quote]
508’s don’t use Client.java.
Login.java or RS2LoginProtocol.java
